Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 1 January 2019. KALI oracle card: KALI - Endings and Beginnings. Quote: The old must be released so that the new can enter. Shows Goddess Kali with third eye open, eclipse/dark moon, lotus flower. Posted on the first day of 2019. CRITICAL: Pure Yug Parivartan philosophy on day one. Aspect: Shakti - Kali ending Kaliyuga so Satyuga can begin.